Time has no count to the amount I announce
These finite assumptions is something I can't pronounce
indoctrination malfunctions when I bounce
Leaping bounds into flights and dismount
Back to the reality dreaming without doubt
Used to be devout now I re route
Any morality clout seeding my soul to not sprout
Not a lazy stout instead
Feeding the spirit the knowledge I am about
Polished filling those cracks like grout
Most branded their lights out
No growth just a slow hand out
Gossiping their fears the plans out
Leaves us all dealing with how it wasn't meant to pan out
Never landing or standing over the hangouts
If you don't speak for yourself watch your damn mouth
